	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "One or other (sources differ), the one a brother, the other a half-brother of Rullianus, spied out northern Etruria and won the aid of Camerinum (Liv. 9.36.2-9, both variants; Frontin. Str. 1.2.2; Flor. 1.11.3)." .
